Now that everything from the winter season finished airing, it's time to do a little wrap-up of the season! For this, I'll be grading every anime I've watched for the season, giving out awards for specific genres and characters, and reveal what I'll be watching for the spring season.

Without further ado, let's get to it!

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/29712345-a060-4db3-a32d-ba547d52af98/1000016207.jpg)

