![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d93cbabe-8021-4caf-9af7-151d4aee2ab6/1000016210.jpg)

**Winter 2025 Overall Thoughts**

At the end of the day, it was a decent season but unfortunately, a good amount of shows were overshadowed by the various shows that were carried over from the previous season. On top of that, only two shows that aired in this season were the only ones that viewers cared about such as _Solo Leveling_ and _Apothecary Diaries_, making the rest be glossed over.

Thankfully, not much carried over into spring, giving plenty of new shows a chance to shine. I'm looking forward to what spring has in store

Score: 7/10

